AGI - The first section of the Court of Cassation has placed an appeal for nine defendants in one of the progeny of the trial for the assault on the headquarters of the Cgil on 9 October 2021. The Supreme Judges annulled with reference the judgments of the Court of Appeal of Rome which had confirmed the convictions, arrived with short rite, of the defendants for the murder of devastation > for the assault on the Cgil, which took place in Rome on 9 October 2021.
